s, and now they're putting up the steel frame. In one section, it's already=
 up to 4 floors tall.</p><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">It looks like they're b=
uilding it the same way they built the main factory. Some parts will probab=
ly be taller than others as construction continues. </p><p style=3D"margin:=
10px 0">They're also expanding the building further south by adding more la=
nd. Once it's finished, this new factory will be a pretty big chunk of the =
size of the main factory (which is 11 million square feet over 1 million sq=
 meters). </p><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">It's turning into another massive =
building. They hope to be finished before summer 2027. Meanwhile Fremont wi=
ll be up sooner and ramp to 1 million humanoids. This 11m sqft place will h=
ave capacity for 10 million humanoids per year. </p><p style=3D"margin:10px=
 0">h.t Joe Tegtmeyer </p><p></p></div></td></tr>
